reviewText: DVDs were burned and would not play on my standard DVD player.
This was a gift and he loved it.
I love Uncle Milty & his crew & this was a very low price from a great seller.  VERY GOOD!
You might say Bob Hope was the king of laguther, but Milton was best of his times. The show makes you laugh no matter what sadness in your life. The Video is not a good quality as some old shows.
